name: Profeshunel (grone-up) Cookeng
description:
Profeshunel Cookeng is a rhythm cooking game about kids in the kitchen! It is two player local PvP and requires two controllers to play. 

Developers: 

Ashley Charlton (art) - https://www.linkedin.com/in/ashley-charlton-695619b1/

Jackie Fazekas (audio) - https://www.linkedin.com/in/jackiefazekas/

Barry Evans (programming) - https://www.linkedin.com/in/barrypaulevans/

Phil Bracco (programming )- https://www.linkedin.com/in/philip-bracco-40576885/
